  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK248">
<l>poruḷaṟṟār pūppa rorukā laruḷaṟṟā</l>
<l>raṟṟārmaṟ ṟāta laritu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who are without wealth may, at some future time, become prosperous; those who are destitute of kindness are utterly destitute; for them there is no change.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
